		{
			"id": "8df51b9c-076f-4c24-aa4f-d9ac11657bea",
			"name": "8df51b9c-076f-4c24-aa4f-d9ac11657bea",
			"type": "therapy",
			"content": {
				"number": "1",
				"title": "Inledande antibiotikabehandling vid sepsis/septisk chock",
				"id": "",
				"text": "<table width=\"633\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"5\" width=\"629\">\r\n<p>F&ouml;rslag p&aring; inledande antibiotikabehandling vid sepsis/septisk chock med utg&aring;ngspunkt fr&aring;n misst&auml;nkt fokus. Preparatval kan beh&ouml;va modifieras f&ouml;r patienter med nedsatt immunf&ouml;rsvar samt vid &ouml;kad risk f&ouml;r infektion med multiresistenta bakterier.<br><br></p>\r\n<p>Vid septisk chock har patienter en &ouml;kad distributionsvolym f&ouml;r vattenl&ouml;sliga antibiotika. F&ouml;r att snabbt uppn&aring; terapeutiska antibiotikakoncentrationer b&ouml;r man d&auml;rf&ouml;r ge en extra dos av betalaktamantibiotika (penicilliner, cefalosporiner och karbapenemer) mellan f&ouml;rsta och andra ordinarie dos.<br><br></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"134\">\r\n<p><strong>Misst&auml;nkt infektionsfokus</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"123\">\r\n<p><strong>Vanliga bakterier</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"189\">\r\n<p><strong>Antibiotikaval</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"76\">\r\n<p><strong>Dosering vuxna </strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"99\">\r\n<p><strong>Dosering barn &gt;&nbsp;1&nbsp;&aring;r </strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td rowspan=\"3\" width=\"134\">\r\n<p><strong>Samh&auml;llsf&ouml;rv&auml;rvad </strong><br> <strong>sv&aring;r pneumoni</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td rowspan=\"3\" width=\"123\">\r\n<p>Streptococcus pneumoniae, Haemophilus influenzae, Legionella pneumophila, Staphylococcus aureus</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"189\">\r\n<p>cefotaxim+</p>\r\n<p>erytromycin+</p>\r\n<p><em>ev.</em></p>\r\n<p>tobramycin&nbsp;eller&nbsp;gentamicin<sup>b</sup></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"76\">\r\n<p>2&nbsp;g&nbsp;x&nbsp;3</p>\r\n<p>1&nbsp;g&nbsp;x&nbsp;3</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>5&ndash;7&nbsp;mg/kg</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"99\">\r\n<p>60&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;3&nbsp; <br> 10&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;4&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>5&ndash;7&nbsp;mg/kg</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"3\" width=\"368\">\r\n<p><em>alternativt</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"189\">\r\n<p>bensylpenicillin +</p>\r\n<p>moxifloxacin <em>eller </em>levofloxacin</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"76\">\r\n<p>3&nbsp;g&nbsp;x&nbsp;4</p>\r\n<p>400&nbsp;mg&nbsp;x&nbsp;1</p>\r\n<p>750&nbsp;mg&nbsp;x&nbsp;1</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"99\">\r\n<p><em>Barn ges normalt ej moxifloxacin/ levofloxacin</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"134\">\r\n<p><strong>Urinv&auml;gar, okomplicerad</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"123\">\r\n<p>Enterobacteriacae<sup>a</sup></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"189\">\r\n<p>cefotaxim +</p>\r\n<p>tobramycin&nbsp;eller&nbsp;gentamicin<sup>b</sup></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"76\">\r\n<p>2&nbsp;g&nbsp;x&nbsp;3</p>\r\n<p>5&ndash;7&nbsp;mg/kg</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"99\">\r\n<p>60&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;3&nbsp; 5&ndash;7&nbsp;mg/kg</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td rowspan=\"3\" width=\"134\">\r\n<p><strong>Urinv&auml;gar, komplicerad (avfl&ouml;deshinder eller KAD)</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td rowspan=\"3\" width=\"123\">\r\n<p>Enterobacteriacae, enterokocker, Pseudomonas aeruginosa</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"189\">\r\n<p>piperacillin-tazobactam +</p>\r\n<p>tobramycin eller gentamicin<sup>b</sup></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"76\">\r\n<p>4&nbsp;g&nbsp;x&nbsp;4&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>5&ndash;7&nbsp;mg/kg</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"99\">\r\n<p>100&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;3</p>\r\n<p>5&ndash;7&nbsp;mg/kg</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"3\" width=\"368\">\r\n<p><em>alternativt</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"189\">\r\n<p>karbapenem<sup>c</sup> +</p>\r\n<p>tobramycin&nbsp;eller&nbsp;gentamicin<sup>b</sup></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"76\">\r\n<p>1&nbsp;g&nbsp;x&nbsp;3-4&nbsp; 5&ndash;7&nbsp;mg/kg</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"99\">\r\n<p>25&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;3 5&ndash;7&nbsp;mg/kg</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td rowspan=\"3\" width=\"134\">\r\n<p><strong>Buk</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td rowspan=\"3\" width=\"123\">\r\n<p>Enterobacteriacae, enterokocker, anaerober</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"189\">\r\n<p>piperacillin-tazobactam +</p>\r\n<p>tobramycin eller gentamicin<sup>b</sup></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"76\">\r\n<p>4&nbsp;g x&nbsp;4</p>\r\n<p>5&ndash;7&nbsp;mg/kg</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"99\">\r\n<p>100&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;3 5&ndash;7&nbsp;mg/kg</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"3\" width=\"368\">\r\n<p><em>alternativt</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"189\">\r\n<p>karbapenem<sup>c</sup> +</p>\r\n<p>tobramycin eller gentamicin<sup>b</sup></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"76\">\r\n<p>1&nbsp;g&nbsp;x&nbsp;3-4</p>\r\n<p>5&ndash;7&nbsp;mg/kg</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"99\">\r\n<p>25&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;3 5&ndash;7&nbsp;mg/kg</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"134\">\r\n<p><strong>Neutropen feber</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"123\">\r\n<p>Streptokocker, Staphylococcus aureus, enterobacteriacae, Pseudomonas aeruginosa</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"189\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>karbapenem<sup>c</sup> +</p>\r\n<p>tobramycin eller gentamicin<sup>b</sup></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"76\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>1&nbsp;g&nbsp;x&nbsp;3-4</p>\r\n<p>5&ndash;7&nbsp;mg/kg</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"99\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>25&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;3 5&ndash;7&nbsp;mg/kg</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td rowspan=\"3\" width=\"134\">\r\n<p><strong>Endokardit</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td rowspan=\"3\" width=\"123\">\r\n<p>Staphylococcus aureus</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"189\">\r\n<p>kloxacillin +</p>\r\n<p>tobramycin eller gentamicin</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"76\">\r\n<p>3&nbsp;g&nbsp;x&nbsp;4 &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>5&ndash;7&nbsp;mg/kg</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"99\">\r\n<p>50&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;4 5&ndash;7&nbsp;mg/kg</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"3\" width=\"368\">\r\n<p><em>alternativt</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"189\">\r\n<p>cefotaxim +</p>\r\n<p>tobramycin eller gentamicin</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"76\">\r\n<p>2&nbsp;g&nbsp;x&nbsp;3</p>\r\n<p>5&ndash;7&nbsp;mg/kg</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"99\">\r\n<p>60&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;3 5&ndash;7&nbsp;mg/kg</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td rowspan=\"3\" width=\"134\">\r\n<p><strong>Ok&auml;nt fokus</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td rowspan=\"3\" width=\"123\">\r\n<p>Streptococcus pneumoniae, Neisseria meningitidis, Staphylococcus aureus,<em> </em>enterobacteriacae m.fl.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"189\">\r\n<p>piperacillin-tazobactam +</p>\r\n<p>tobramycin eller gentamicin<sup>b</sup></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"76\">\r\n<p>4&nbsp;g&nbsp;x&nbsp;4&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 5&ndash;7&nbsp;mg/kg</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"99\">\r\n<p>100&nbsp;mg/kg x&nbsp;3 5&ndash;7&nbsp;mg/kg</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"3\" width=\"368\">\r\n<p><em>alternativt</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"189\">\r\n<p>cefotaxim +</p>\r\n<p>tobramycin eller gentamicin<sup>b</sup></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"76\">\r\n<p>2&nbsp;g&nbsp;x&nbsp;3&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>5&ndash;7&nbsp;mg/kg</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"99\">\r\n<p>60&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;3 5&ndash;7&nbsp;mg/kg</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"3\" width=\"450\">\r\n<p><strong>Neonatal sepsis</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td colspan=\"2\" width=\"177\">\r\n<p><strong>Dosering</strong><sup>d</sup></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"134\">\r\n<p><em>&lt;&nbsp;72 h efter partus</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"123\">\r\n<p>Grupp B-streptokocker, enterobacteriacae</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"189\">\r\n<p>bensylpenicillin +</p>\r\n<p>tobramycin eller gentamicin</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td colspan=\"2\" width=\"177\">\r\n<p>50-100&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;3-4<sup>e</sup></p>\r\n<p>5&nbsp;mg/kg var 24-36:e tim<sup>e</sup></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"134\">\r\n<p><em>&gt;&nbsp;72 h efter partus</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"123\">\r\n<p>Som ovan + KNS m.fl.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"189\">\r\n<p>cefotaxim +</p>\r\n<p>tobramycin eller gentamicin</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td colspan=\"2\" width=\"177\">\r\n<p>50&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;2-3<sup>e</sup></p>\r\n<p>5&nbsp;mg/kg var 24-36:e tim<sup>e</sup></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"5\" width=\"629\">\r\n<p>a. Enterobacteriacae innefattar bl.a. Escherichia coli, Klebsiella pneumoniae och Proteus mirabilis.</p>\r\n<p>b. Vid k&auml;nt b&auml;rarskap eller riskfaktor f&ouml;r ESBL (nyligen vistats i h&ouml;gendemiskt omr&aring;de) ges ist&auml;llet amikacin i dosering 25&ndash;30&nbsp;mg/kg</p>\r\n<p>c. Med karbapenemer avses h&auml;r meropenem eller imipenem och cilastatin f&ouml;r vuxen, f&ouml;r barn avses meropenem</p>\r\n<p>d. G&auml;ller f&ouml;r gestations&aring;lder &ge;&nbsp;33 veckor vid partus</p>\r\n<p>e. Dosering beroende av vikt och &aring;lder. R&aring;dg&ouml;r med specialist.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p></p>"
