			"name": "fc889b0f-7a3b-4e2b-8424-49161996a4be",
			"type": "facts",
			"content": {
				"number": "8",
				"title": "Typiska nivåer för kemiska likvoranalyser vid akut bakteriell meningit respektive viral meningit/encefalit",
				"text": "<table width=\"100%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>Analys</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>Akut bakteriell meningit</strong><sup>a</sup></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>Viral meningit/encefalit</strong><sup>a</sup></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Grumlig likvor?</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>oftast grumlig</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>aldrig grumlig</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Likvortryck (cm&nbsp;H<sub>2</sub>0)</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>oftast &ge;&nbsp;20</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>oftast &lt;&nbsp;20</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Leukocyter (x&nbsp;10<sup>6</sup>/l)</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>&gt;&nbsp;500</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>&lt;&nbsp;500</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Polymorfk&auml;rniga vs. mononukle&auml;ra leukocyter</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>polydominans</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>monodominans</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Glukos (mmol/l)</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>&lt;&nbsp;2</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>&gt;&nbsp;2</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Glukoskvot (likvor/plasma)</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>&le;&nbsp;0,4</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>&gt;&nbsp;0,4</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Albumin (mg/l)</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>&gt;&nbsp;1000</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>&lt;&nbsp;1000</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Laktat (mmol/l)</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>&ge;&nbsp;3,5</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>&lt;&nbsp;3,5</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"3\">\r\n<p><sup>a</sup> V&auml;rdena anger endast <em>typiska</em> niv&aring;er/koncentrationer. Det f&ouml;rekommer exempelvis ov&auml;ntat l&aring;ga celltal i vissa fall av ABM och vid lumbarpunktion ett par dagar efter p&aring;b&ouml;rjad antibiotikabehandling mot ABM ses ofta en &ldquo;viral&rdquo; likvorprofil.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p></p>",
