		{
			"id": "05ec2132-7370-4fec-97c5-b0bf4c034f7a",
			"name": "05ec2132-7370-4fec-97c5-b0bf4c034f7a",
			"type": "therapy",
			"content": {
				"number": "2",
				"title": " Förslag till intravenös antibiotikabehandling vid akut bakteriell meningit",
				"id": "",
				"text": "<table width=\"667\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"181\">\r\n<p><strong>Bakgrund/bakterie</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"119\">\r\n<p><strong>Antibiotika</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"119\">\r\n<p><strong>Dosering vuxna</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"110\">\r\n<p><strong>Dosering barn</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"129\">\r\n<p><strong>Behandlingstid</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td rowspan=\"3\" width=\"181\">\r\n<p><strong>Inledande behandling</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"119\">\r\n<p>cefotaxim + ampicillin<sup>a</sup></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"119\">\r\n<p>3&nbsp;g&nbsp;x&nbsp;4</p>\r\n<p>3&nbsp;g&nbsp;x&nbsp;4</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"110\">\r\n<p>75&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;4 50&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;4</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"129\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"3\" width=\"349\">\r\n<p><em>alternativt</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"129\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"119\">\r\n<p>meropenem</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"119\">\r\n<p>2&nbsp;g&nbsp;x&nbsp;3</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"110\">\r\n<p>40&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;3</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"129\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"5\" width=\"663\">\r\n<p>Vid <strong>l&aring;ng transportv&auml;g</strong> (&gt;&nbsp;60 min) kan prehospital antibiotikabehandling &ouml;verv&auml;gas (cefotaxim 3&nbsp;g alternativt ceftriaxon 4&nbsp;g)</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"181\">\r\n<p>Vid <em>allvarlig &ouml;verk&auml;nslighet</em><sup>b </sup>mot betalaktam-antibiotika <sup>c</sup></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"119\">\r\n<p>moxifloxacin + vancomycin</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"119\">\r\n<p>400&nbsp;mg&nbsp;x&nbsp;1</p>\r\n<p>1&nbsp;g&nbsp;x&nbsp;3</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"110\">\r\n<p>10&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;1</p>\r\n<p>20&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;3</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"129\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td rowspan=\"3\" width=\"181\">\r\n<p><em>Streptococcus pneumoniae</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"119\">\r\n<p>bensylpenicillin</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"119\">\r\n<p>3&nbsp;g&nbsp;x&nbsp;4</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"110\">\r\n<p>60&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;4</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td rowspan=\"3\" width=\"129\">\r\n<p>10&ndash;14 dagar</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"3\" width=\"349\">\r\n<p><em>alternativt</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"119\">\r\n<p>cefotaxim</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"119\">\r\n<p>3&nbsp;g&nbsp;x&nbsp;4</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"110\">\r\n<p>75&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;4</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"181\">\r\n<p><em>Neisseria meningitidis</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"119\">\r\n<p>bensylpenicillin</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"119\">\r\n<p>3&nbsp;g&nbsp;x&nbsp;4</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"110\">\r\n<p>60&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;4</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"129\">\r\n<p>7 dagar</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"181\">\r\n<p><em>Haemophilus influenzae</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"119\">\r\n<p>cefotaxim</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"119\">\r\n<p>3&nbsp;g&nbsp;x&nbsp;4</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"110\">\r\n<p>75&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;4</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"129\">\r\n<p>10&ndash;14 dagar</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"181\">\r\n<p><em>Staphylococcus aureus</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"119\">\r\n<p>cefuroxim+<br> rifampicin</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"119\">\r\n<p>3&nbsp;g&nbsp;x&nbsp;4</p>\r\n<p>600&nbsp;mg&nbsp;x&nbsp;1</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"110\">\r\n<p>50&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;4</p>\r\n<p>15&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;1</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"129\">\r\n<p>14&ndash;21 dagar</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"181\">\r\n<p><em>Listeria monocytogenes</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"119\">\r\n<p>ampicillin</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"119\">\r\n<p>3&nbsp;g&nbsp;x&nbsp;4</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"110\">\r\n<p>50&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;4</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"129\">\r\n<p>14&ndash;21 dagar</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td rowspan=\"3\" width=\"181\">\r\n<p><em>Escherichia coli/Klebsiella pneumoniae</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"119\">\r\n<p>cefotaxim</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"119\">\r\n<p>3&nbsp;g&nbsp;x&nbsp;4</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"110\">\r\n<p>75&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;4</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td rowspan=\"3\" width=\"129\">\r\n<p>14&ndash;21 dagar</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"3\" width=\"349\">\r\n<p><em>alternativt</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"119\">\r\n<p>meropenem</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"119\">\r\n<p>2&nbsp;g&nbsp;x&nbsp;3</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"110\">\r\n<p>40&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;3</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"5\" width=\"663\">\r\n<p>a. Till&auml;gg av ampicillin till cefotaxim till barn &lt;&nbsp;3&nbsp;m&aring;n, till patienter &gt;&nbsp;5&nbsp;&aring;r samt till immunsupprimerade individer f&ouml;r att &auml;ven t&auml;cka <em>L. monocytogenes<br><br></em></p>\r\n<p>b. Allvarlig &ouml;verk&auml;nslighet inneb&auml;r angio&ouml;dem, luftv&auml;gsobstruktivitet eller anafylaktisk chock</p>\r\n<p>c. Vid risk f&ouml;r <em>L. monocytogenes</em> (enligt a) ges &auml;ven trimetoprim-sufametoxazol (Eusaprim koncentrat till infusionsv&auml;tska, l&ouml;sning 16&nbsp;mg/ml + 80&nbsp;mg/ml) 20&nbsp;ml&nbsp;x&nbsp;2 intraven&ouml;st till vuxen (barn 0,375&nbsp;ml/kg kroppsvikt x&nbsp;2 intraven&ouml;st)<br><br></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>"
			},
